snippet.title: Belonging | Demo Gameplay | No Commentary
snippet.description:
Belonging is a first-person adventure game where you play as Jayce, a hacktivist exploring the remnants of the Entelechism cult. Uncover the dark truths behind this seemingly innocent community focused on self-optimization, revealing manipulative control and hidden secrets. 

---------------

Belonging - Demo (2023)

Release Date: 18 Jan, 2024
Developer/Publisher: Farbspiel Interactive 

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2081580/Belonging/
